Paper: hep-th/0110265

Date: 2001-10-29

Title: A black hole hologram in de Sitter space

Authors: Ulf H. Danielsson

Comments: 13 pages. Final version accepted for publication in JHEP. Added

references and improved presentationJournal-ref: JHEP 0203 (2002) 020

In this paper we show that the entropy of de Sitter space with a black holein arbitrary dimension can be understood using a modified Cardy-Verlindeentropy formula. We also comment on the observer dependence of the de Sitterentropy.